Correspondence: P. C. Y. Woo, MD, State Key Laboratory of Emerging Infectious Diseases, Department of Microbiology, The University of Hong Kong, Room 423, University Pathology Building, Queen Mary Hospital, Hong Kong, China (

 pcywoo@hku.hk

).

